{"tid":2374758,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當選新一屆大律師公會主席　人權大狀夏博義：我會保護香港自由","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T14:06:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"892873c58750dc27aa5d965b9d1adb855efc7dd2","tid":2374758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"大律師公會今（21 日）換屆，曾兩度連任主席的戴啟思（Philip Dykes）按憲章規定須卸任，「香港人權監察」創會主席、資深大律師夏博義（Paul Harris）無競爭下接棒。現任副主席、資深大律師葉巧琦連任成功，另一名副主席為原任執委的大律師沈士文。<br />\n<br />\n夏博義當選後，手持象徵主席身份的木椅模型，在場外見記者，他表示，大律師公會及香港法治均正面臨艱難的時期，作為委身（deeply committed）法律的大律師，他不支持暴力示威者，同時亦不支持政府濫權，會在任期內盡力強化法治精神。<br />\n<br />\n他亦提到，自己尤為關注部分國安法條文，特別是當中提到部分官方權力凌駕於法律之上，很多國家亦因為對國安法的憂慮，已取消與香港的引渡協議，意味著犯了法的人，如謀殺者，可以輕易逃避法律制裁，尤其在疫情後出入境將更容易，那是所有人都不願看見，因此他會盡力協商，希望政府可以同意修改部分國安法條文，令引渡協議可以恢復，「我不知道是否可能，但我會嘗試。（I don&rsquo;t know if that would be possible, but that&rsquo;s what I&rsquo;m going to work towards.）」<br />\n<br />\n他又用中文說，「我好擔心香港嘅自由唔會繼續，我會嘗試保護香港嘅自由，我會盡力。我唔知道我會否成功。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9-%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcHjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=bdb76199\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&h=b5a9a17f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9-%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"4f6fdf678db3c117fc39b66b6ab9cfefdcb0f304","tid":2374758,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"會在任期內盡力強化<span class=\"red\">共產黨以法統治</span>精神"},{"pid":"821d7f67dc56d7e17ccb9a2fd2f8e2d31687fbc1","tid":2374758,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce0075cde6b08a5d3cfab420bab3bba4517beda","tid":2374758,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fedc36da48a2385d56f0d3f6adb1e52156b2917","tid":2374758,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"//因此他會盡力協商，希望政府可以同意修改部分國安法條文，令引渡協議可以恢復，「我不知道是否可能，但我會嘗試。（I don&rsquo;t know if that would be possible, but that&rsquo;s what I&rsquo;m going to work towards.）」//<br />\n<br />\n只豝Paul Harris一日仲在世 咁天真嬌喺香港頂多都只係排第二最天真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc352f7b1a5d37952c04507aff7bc7cb7446674f","tid":2374758,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"大律師公會傍晚舉行周年大會，改選正副主席及部份執委，會議進行不足1小時便結束，資深大律師駱應淦、李柱銘、李志喜等都有出席，剛卸下主席職務的戴啟思也有到場。會上由有人權大狀之稱的資深大律師夏博義在沒有競爭下當選主席，資深大律師葉巧琦及大律師沈士文則擔任副主席，另外5名執委改選，現任執委梁寶琳和蘇諾賢成功連任，新加入則有資深大律師陳政龍、大律師陳志剛及馬亞山。"},{"pid":"dbacec231fa3ea49320e9929e6287ed9dcaa18df","tid":2374758,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"又係Harris<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}